item.title: Featuring
item.description: Some online pages featuring me. My paper: General Additive Network Effect Model was featured in the “Design and Analysis of Experiments for Data Science” webinar by the New England Journal of Statistics in Data Science. I appeared on the news of the Statistical Consulting and Survey Research Unit for my collaborative paper on tax fairness and tax compliance. 2023 CANSSI International Day of Women and Girls in Science. KAIST Best Undergraduate Thesis Award.
